Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.39,0:00:28.73,ScreenText,,0,0,0,,{\fad(180,0)\be1\c&HFFE37C&\3c&HF23519&}主題曲{\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&} & {\c&HFF0300&\3c&HFBF6F5&}插曲{\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&} 介紹！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.67,0:00:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,從各個角度
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.10,0:00:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,來體味動畫Charlotte的魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.73,0:00:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,看了這個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.63,0:00:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,希望你能開啟
